7/the-uschina-ai-arms-race-has-taken-an-unexpected-turn</link><description>中国企业打造的强大人工智能模型从引起广泛恐慌到耸耸肩——是什么改变了？ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-uschina-ai-arms-race-has-taken-an-unexpected-turn.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 12:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-uschina-ai-arms-race-has-taken-an-unexpected-turn</guid></item><item><title>糖衣纳米颗粒缩小了小鼠致命的脑肿瘤</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/sugar-coated-nanoparticles-shrink-deadly-brain-tumors-in-mice</link><description>癌症并不比癌症更严重&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/sugar-coated-nanoparticles-shrink-deadly-brain-tumors-in-mice.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 12:18:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/sugar-coated-nanoparticles-shrink-deadly-brain-tumors-in-mice</guid></item><item><title>硬膜外麻醉不会增加新生儿或儿童的伤害</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/epidurals-not-linked-to-increased-harm-for-newborns-or-children</link><description>根据《英国医学杂志》发表的一项研究，在分娩过程中进行硬膜外麻醉与临床上显着增加新生儿受到伤害的风险无关，这些风险包括脑损伤、严重呼吸问题、败血症和死亡，或儿童后期脑瘫。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/epidurals-not-linked-to-increased-harm-for-newborns-or-children2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 12:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/epidurals-not-linked-to-increased-harm-for-newborns-or-children</guid></item><item><title>隐形可穿戴设备：新型皮肤传感器推进健康监测</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-invisible-wearable-new-skin-sensors-advance-health-monitoring</link><description>虽然可穿戴健康传感器变得越来越普遍，但当前的迭代产品佩戴起来很尴尬。例如，附着在脸上的设备可能会引起不必要的注意，增加自我意识并影响用户试图测量的信号。然而，最近的研究可能通过引入观察者看不见或佩戴者感觉不到的超薄传感器找到了解决方案。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-invisible-wearable-new-skin-sensors-advance-health-monitoring2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 11:48:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-invisible-wearable-new-skin-sensors-advance-health-monitoring</guid></item><item><title>效应器 ORFeome 平台识别新途径</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/effector-orfeome-platform-identifies-novel-pathways</link><description>为了防止病毒使我们生病或杀死我们——无论是乙型肝炎个案还是新冠病毒大流行——了解它们产生的蛋白质如何引发我们身体的变化，从而使它们蓬勃发展是至关重要的。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/effector-orfeome-platform-identifies-novel-pathways.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 11:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/effector-orfeome-platform-identifies-novel-pathways</guid></item><item><title>索马鲁肽可能会减缓表观遗传衰老的速度</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/semaglutide-may-slow-the-pace-of-epigenetic-aging</link><description>虽然GLP-1药物可以抑制&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/semaglutide-may-slow-the-pace-of-epigenetic-aging2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 11:18:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/semaglutide-may-slow-the-pace-of-epigenetic-aging</guid></item><item><title>局部信号，系统性衰退</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/local-signals-systemic-decline</link><description>高脂肪饮食影响肿瘤到神经的信号传导并促进小鼠恶病质&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/local-signals-systemic-decline2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 11:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/local-signals-systemic-decline</guid></item></channel></rss>